  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Uninterrupted Power for Your Dream Wall",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Dream Wall Power Module is an essential accessory for a Dream Wall device, providing power redundancy and ensuring continuous operation in the event of a power outage. This reliable power module seamlessly integrates with the UDW, offering an additional layer of protection for your critical network infrastructure. The Dream Wall Power Module functions as a secondary power source for your Dream Wall, safeguarding your network from unexpected power disruptions. With its 550W (54.8V) AC-to-DC auxiliary power supply, the module provides ample power to maintain the operation of your Dream Wall and its connected devices."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Seamless Integration",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Dream Wall Power Module is designed for effortless integration with your existing Dream Wall setup. The module easily connects to the UDW, providing a seamless power backup solution. With its plug-and-play functionality, you can quickly add power redundancy to your Dream Wall without any hassle. With its redundant power supply, unmatched compatibility, and easy installation, the Dream Wall Power Module is an essential addition to any Dream Wall deployment."
    }
  ],
